? display help                         j Display next message
. Display current message              k Display previous message
+ Next index page                      l List the available nodes
- Previous index page                  m Mail message
$ Resynchronize folder                 n Display next message
= First is current                     o Option system
* Last is current                      p Display previous message
# Supply current message number        Q Quick quit
a Alias system                         q Quit
b Bounce message                       r Reply to message
C Copy to folder                       S Save to .mbox (wiz only)
c Change folder                        s Save to folder
d Delete message                       u Undelete message
F Display folders                      w Write to file (wiz only)
f Forward message                      X Quick exit
h Display message with header          x Exit
i Display current index page
